  <para>What is it? The BlipBox is all of the following:</para>

  <itemizedlist>
    <listitem><para>a creative tool and musical instrument</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>a large, high definition x/y controller with visual feedback</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>a uniquely versatile <ulink url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Midi">MIDI</ulink> and <ulink url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenSound_Control">OSC</ulink> controller</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>a <ulink url="http://monome.org/">monome</ulink> emulator</para></listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

